songs.title: Stronger [What Doesn’t Kill You] (Cover)
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1: Lauren]
You know the bed feels warmer
Sleeping here alone
You know I dream in color
And do the things I want

[Pre-Chorus: Lauren]
You think you got the best of me, think you've had the last laugh
Bet you think that everything good is gone
Think you left me broken down, think that I'd come running back
Baby you don't know me cause you're dead wrong

[Chorus: All]
What doesn't kill you makes you stronger, stand a little taller
Doesn't mean I'm lonely when I'm alone
What doesn't kill you makes a fighter, footsteps even lighter
Doesn't mean I'm over cause you're gone
What doesn't kill you makes you stronger, stronger
Just me, myself, and I
What doesn't kill you makes you stronger, stand a little taller
Doesn't mean I'm lonely when I'm alone

[Verse 2: Lauren]
You heard that I was starting over with someone new
They told you I was moving on, over you

[Pre-Chorus 2: All]
You didn't think that I'd come back, I'd come back swinging
You tried to break me, but you see

[Chorus: All]
What doesn't kill you makes you stronger, stand a little taller
Doesn't mean I'm lonely when I'm alone
What doesn't kill you makes a fighter, footsteps even lighter
Doesn't mean I'm over cause you're gone
What doesn't kill you makes you stronger, stronger
Just me, myself, and I
What doesn't kill you makes you stronger, stand a little taller
Doesn't mean I'm lonely when I'm alone

[Bridge: Dinah]
Thanks to you I got a new thing started
Thanks to you I'm not the broken-hearted
Thanks to you I'm finally thinking about me
You know in the end the day you left was just my beginning

[Chorus: All & Dinah]
What doesn't kill you makes you stronger, stand a little taller
Doesn't mean I'm lonely when I'm alone
What doesn't kill you makes a fighter, footsteps even lighter
(Fighter)
Doesn't mean I'm over cause you're gone
What doesn't kill you makes you stronger, stronger
Just me, myself, and I
What doesn't kill you makes you stronger, stand a little taller
Doesn't mean I'm lonely when I'm alone
What doesn't kill you makes you stronger
